---

<section class="bg-navy-900 text-white py-section">
  <div class="container-narrow grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-center">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow text-white/60 mb-4">HOUSEMAN OS</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-h2 text-white tracking-tight mb-7">
        범용 SaaS가 못한 걸,<br/>
